longBusinessSummary: Elva International, Inc. engages in the design, production, and marketing of security products primarily used in notebooks, desktops, and fixed and cellular phones in the United States. The company, through its VocalID technology, develops and offers VocalID smartcard products for general purpose online security level authentication process; and VocalAccess products for the replacement of the traditional Winlogon service. It sells its products primarily to the original equipment manufacturers and their suppliers operating in the computer, communication, and industrial markets. Elva International was founded in 1997. The company is headquartered in Boulogne-Billancourt, France.
